name: Army
description: $ARMY is more than a meme — it’s a movement. Inspired by the unity of frogs and toads (an “army” in nature), this Solana-based token rallies holders to join the ranks, fight for glory, and dominate the meme coin trenches. Launched on pump.fun, $ARMY blends humor, community culture, and meme mastery with a bold vision for the future. Built for believers, $ARMY is a rally cry for those ready to stand together, create viral moments, and rewrite the meme coin narrative. Soon we will rule every timeline, top every leaderboard, and take the trenches once and for all. Long live the $ARMY!
